Oval Origami Basket is a decorative container folded from a square sheet of paper, featuring a smooth oval rim, straight sides, and a structured base.

## Result

![](/diagram-images/origami-oval-basket/result-origami-oval-basket.png)

\## Reference\
\
This version is based on the model demonstrated in the following video: \
[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pMNqOaglQas](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pMNqOaglQas)\
\
\## Notes\
\
In this interpretation, I refined the proportions and defined the measurements more precisely, ensuring that the model works consistently with a perfect square sheet.\
